info.title: Maintenance Order - Read
info.description:
This service enables you to retrieve maintenance order data. It contains order header, operation, component, object list item and operation relationship nodes. The service is based on the OData protocol, and can be consumed in external systems, Fiori applications and on other user interfaces.
If there are any issues when retrieving the maintenance order data, the system displays appropriate warning or error messages in the response

x-sap-shortText: Read maintenance order data synchronously using this inbound service
